casebody.data:
Ion POZDERCA, Personal Representative of the Estate of Diana E. Pozderca, Deceased, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
MAPLE LANE GOLF CLUB and Bearcat Enterprises, Inc., d/b/a Buffalo Wild Wings, Defendants-Appellees,
and
Tad Dennis, Defendant. SC: 158112
COA: 341709 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 4, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the June 7, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
